Background

		Mr. Bjorn Sibbern has been an Executive Vice President of Global Information Services at Nasdaq, Inc. October 10, 2016. Mr. Sibbern served as a Senior Vice President of Commodities Markets and Broker Services at Nasdaq, Inc until October 10, 2016. Mr. Sibbern served as  President of NASDAQ OMX Copenhagen A/S since April 2008. He served as Head - Sales efforts for cash equities and equities derivatives of The Nasdaq OMX Group, Inc. since November 10, 2008 and served as ... its President of NASDAQ OMX Copenhagen and Senior Vice President of Equities Markets. He served as Vice President for Issuer Service at the Nordic Exchange as well as Head of Trading and Issuer Services at OMX Nordic Exchange Copenhagen. Mr. Sibbern holds an Executive MBA, a Diploma in Business Administration and an MSc in Economics & Business Administration and Law from Copenhagen Business School.Read Full Background




